ws.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3396128</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">連登仔：恐懼撚大驚小怪，感冒黎架姐<br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"未有肺炎之前喺街行<br />\n你見到香港人好正常？"},{"pid":"235e46bb7224a1664115321494d61665755fcff5","tid":2346302,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">根據《紐約時報》報導</span></span><br />\n<br />\n留名等睇 又有人屌柒自由時報係fake news<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bc1c35c2d1dd6e53e83b8ccadace602b71d413","tid":2346302,"uid":358542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"我要殺晒你哋班連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：中過武肺"},{"pid":"421f079c2c336fbc7913d3ae2ab8947759860db9","tid":2346302,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"04bc1c35c2d1dd6e53e83b8ccadace602b71d413","tid":2346302,"uid":358542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"我要殺晒你哋班連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：中過武肺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n癲佬出現了"},{"pid":"376b1560b3708b7f4f104887133e1981e557b3d4","tid":2346302,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:23:09.000Z","msg":"笑死 又係呢啲滑坡研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港平時都大把精神病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cba2f2dc5b1a758fca8d34ca882124919699045","tid":2346302,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:29:26.000Z","msg":"精神病人中武肺"},{"pid":"19541701037fe37b340bb0f754563261ee1f8f34","tid":2346302,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"偏執狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />病毒公司"},{"pid":"626ec51c2508494d851b9b0ba66c90aaca819f1a","tid":2346302,"uid":29917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:31:40.000Z","msg":"有無諗過其實唔係精神病，係武肺之後聽剄來自外星既聲音"},{"pid":"e6fd85c56afa83349b10f85e883cc9957ef8662d","tid":2346302,"uid":69120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"懷疑係佢地精神壓力太大 （ 因為失業 好多野加埋<br />\n搞到有精神病多 <br />\n<br />\n唔係武肺直接導致<br />\n而係間接 （ 令經濟差 好多人死 無哂社交"}],"pinned":{"pid":"04bc1c35c2d1dd6e53e83b8ccadace602b71d413","tid":2346302,"uid":358542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"我要殺晒你哋班連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：中過武肺"}}